# Implementation Plan — Tantangan Tambahan

## 1. Husky Pre-commit Hook (Lint + Format)

### Latar Belakang
Husky dipasang di root workspace (`c:\...\capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter`), bukan di dalam `server/`. Hook akan memblokir commit jika ada error lint dari ESLint dan Prettier.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> ESLint sudah ada di `server/`. Prettier **belum** ada sebagai dependency — perlu ditambahkan.

### Proposed Changes

#### [MODIFY] Root [package.json](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/package.json) (file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/package.json)
- Tambahkan `scripts`:
  ```json
  "prepare": "husky",
  "lint": "cd server && npm run lint && cd ../client && npm run lint",
  "format": "prettier --write \"server/src/**/*.js\" \"client/src/**/*.{jsx,js,css}\""
  ```
- Tambahkan `devDependencies`:
  ```json
  "husky": "^9.x",
  "lint-staged": "^15.x",
  "prettier": "^3.x"
  ```

#### [NEW] `.husky/pre-commit`
Hook shell script yang dijalankan sebelum setiap `git commit`:
```sh
npx lint-staged
```

#### [NEW] `.lintstagedrc.json` di root
Konfigurasi menentukan perintah yang dijalankan per jenis file:
```json
{
  "server/src/**/*.js": ["eslint --fix", "prettier --write"],
  "client/src/**/*.{js,jsx,css}": ["prettier --write"]
}
```

#### [NEW] `.prettierrc` di root
Konfigurasi format standar:
```json
{
  "singleQuote": true,
  "semi": true,
  "trailingComma": "es5",
  "printWidth": 100
}
```

#### [MODIFY] [server/.eslintrc.json](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/.eslintrc.json)  
Tambahkan rule `prettier/prettier` agar ESLint dan Prettier tidak konflik (opsional, tapi recommended).

### Verification
```bash
# Install packages
npm install  # di root

# Coba commit file apa saja dengan error lint → harus GAGAL
# Coba commit file clean → harus BERHASIL
git add server/src/services/llm.js && git commit -m "test hook"
```

